item.title: Ukulele Player Design Hazel Retro Handwriting & Uke Drawing
item.description: A cool retro design for ukulele players showing the word Ukulele in a handwritten script font and a simple uke drawing “underlining” it. Share your love for this awesome Hawaiian instrument with this 70s style design on a shirt or one of the available products. It also makes for a nice birthday present or Christmas gift for family and friends. • Millions of unique designs by independent artists. Find your thing.

item.title: Recommended Online Resources and Tools for Guitar Players
item.description: On this page I share my favorite online resources and tools for guitar players.

item.title: Manu Chao - La Vida Tómbola
item.description: La Vida Tómbola is a song from Manu Chao about the Argentine football legend Diego Armando Maradona from the album La Radiolina.

item.title: Gsus Saves - Ukulele Player Heavy Metal Blue/Black Design
item.description: This design is for ukulele players who enjoy heavy metal music and a terrible pun. It shows a Gsus4 (G suspended) chord diagram for an Ukulele in GCEA tuning and the word SAVES in a heavy metal style font. Great for concerts, festivals and other places where you meet people who love music. • Also buy this artwork on apparel, stickers, phone cases, and more.
